            <abstract id="ref3" label="Abstract">The collection contains materials collected by Joseph Gayol, an activist in rank and file movements in the Transport Workers Union of America, Local 100. The collection is comprised largely of campaign flyers and circulars distributed to Local 100 members by dissident rank and file candidates. Also included are grievance forms, correspondence, contracts and agreements.</abstract>
